{
  "text": "A standard approach to obtaining the SVR solution is to solve a quadratic programming problem derived as the dual problem of Eq. [CITATION_1] . Recently, it was shown that linear SVR can be efficiently solved with the bundle methods for regularized empirical risk minimization [CITATION_2] . For this approach, see Section 4.2.1.",
